% Test: Drop Current Knowledge Graph Error
% Category: 01_knowledge_graph
% Description: Tests that dropping the currently active KG produces an error

% Create and switch to a new KG
.kg create test_drop_current
.kg use test_drop_current

% Add some data
+test_data[(1, "data")].
?- test_data(X, Y).

% Try to drop the current KG - should error
.kg drop test_drop_current

% Cleanup (switch away first)
.kg use default
.kg drop test_drop_current
